    "Headline": "#78 Montrose, #76 Diversey, #77 Belmont, #80 Irving Park & #152 Addison Temporary Reroute at Montrose/Austin",
    "ShortDescription": "#78. #76, #77, #80 & #152 buses are temporarily rerouted via Montrose, Narragansett, Irving Park, Central & Montrose due to street blockage near Montrose/Austin",
